nodes.text: Hengin Ki-Tapp Wett Gon-far was a Gazaran tree-city built in the rainsforests of Veron. Located on the southeastern coast of the Vusl continent, and while it wasn't the largest city of the Gazaran, it was one of the most powerful. The city controlled the nearby Treblio spaceport, strictly regulating what business the other cities could do in that area. The city had a population of over 100,000 Gazaran.
